	/// Percentage of service sessions with an outcome of "Hangup By Customer" AND a duration below SLA, out of all the service sessions that have an outcome of  "Hangup By Customer"
	/// 
	/// %HangupSLA = DIVIDE([ΣHangupInQueueSLA],[ΣHangupByCustomer(OG)]) * 100
	measure %HangupSLA = DIVIDE([ΣHangupInQueueSLA],[ΣHangupByCustomer(OG)]) * 100
		formatString: 0.0
		lineageTag: 9748fa61-f39f-47f1-83d4-76a57e8cefaf

